{
    "Sender": "{sender's public key}",
    "Recipient": "{recipient's public key}",
    "Amount": {amount to send},
	"Signature": "{signature}"
}

transactions can be created through {ipAddress:port}/brasscoin/api/transactions/new

Sender can be replaced with "me"(in lowercase) to use the account already logged in
Signature is not required if sender is "me" or is the public key of the account currently logged in.